{
  "day": "1",
  "heading": "Arrive at Manali. Drive from Manali to Gulaba Roadhead via Palchan. Trek to Jonker Thatch",
  "sub_heading": "Drive Distance: 24 km | Drive Duration: 1 hour |Trek Distance: 1.5 km | Trek Duration: 1.5 hrs\nAltitude Gain: 6,725 ft to 10,285 ft",
  "details": "Leave from Beas Bridge, Manali, Manali at 10.00 AM for Gulaba. En route, at Palchan, drop your cloakroom bag and collect your rentals. You will meet your trek leader here where he will brief you about the trek. Make sure that you complete your lunch before reaching Gulaba.\nIndiahikes will arrange transport for the transfer from Manali to Gulaba. This pickup costs ₹900 (additional 5% GST) per trekker one way from Manali to Gulaba (₹1800 for onward and return journeys). These are non-AC vehicles. Please pre-book your transport through the dashboard before your trek.\nYour trek starts from Gulaba. From there, you reach the first campsite at Jonker Thatch around 3.30 PM."
}

{
  "day": "2",
  "heading": "Trek from Jonker Thatch to Rola Kholi",
  "sub_heading": "Trek Distance: 5 km | Trek Duration: 3-4 hours | Altitude Gain: 10,285 ft to 12,590 ft",
  "details": "Moderate. Steep ascent throughout followed by an undulating walk for the last 30 minutes."
}

{
  "day": "3",
  "heading": "Trek from Rola Kholi to Bhrigu Lake, and back to Rola Kholi",
  "sub_heading": "Trek Distance: 10 km | Trek Duration: 7-8 hours | Altitude Gain and Loss: 12,590 ft to 14,009 ft and back",
  "details": "Moderate. Starts on a stony trail. Initial ascent for 2 hours followed by 10 minutes descent. Level walk for 15 minutes followed by an hour’s steep ascent to the lake."
}

{
  "day": "4",
  "heading": "Trek from Rola Kholi to Gulaba. Drive back to Manali",
  "sub_heading": "Trek Distance: 5 km | Trek Duration: 3-4 hours\nAltitude Loss: 12,590 ft to 9,875 ft",
  "details": "Easy. Mostly descending all the way to Gulaba.\nIndiahikes will arrange transport for the drop-off to Manali from Gulaba. This drop-off costs ₹900 (additional 5% GST) per trekker one way from Gulaba to Manali (₹1800 for onward and return journeys). These are non-AC vehicles. Please pre-book your transport through the dashboard before your trek.\nOn the way back, stop at Palchan, collect your cloakroom and return rentals.\nYou are expected to reach Manali by 4 PM.\nPlease note: The distance between campsites may vary by 100 meters depending the weather conditions and the route you take. The altitude may also vary by 100 feet for similar reasons."
}
